(36, '2', '硕士', '2013年工商管理专业（战略管理与营销创新方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '￥24000', '2013-03-02', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548866323949.png" /><img title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548866327405.jpg" width="275" height="60" />&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班工商管理专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（战略管理与营销创新方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对人力资源工作岗位职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办工商管理专业（战略管理与营销创新方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>60<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">自然辩证法概论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="5" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代管理理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">战略管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">市场营销管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">财务管理理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">人力资源管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">技术创新管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">品牌管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理沟通</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">员工关系管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">消费行为学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">项目管理</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学社会主义理论与实践</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科学技术哲学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="5" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代管理理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">战略管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">市场营销管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">财务管理理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">人力资源管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">会计理论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">高级计量经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">技术经济评价理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="3" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理沟通</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">员工关系管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="color:black;font-family:宋体;">渠道管理</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:black;font-family:宋体;">项目管理</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="color:black;font-family:宋体;">品牌管理</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:black;font-family:宋体;">经营\\创新管理</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 75px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名及注册时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1331</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1332</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1333</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1334</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">10</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">16</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">24000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">注：</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">2012</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">年</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">12</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">月</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">日前</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">报名学员执行学费</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">20000</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">标准</span></strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院主楼二层</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-align:center;line-height:29px;"><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886664);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`cid`, `type`, `level`, `name`, `price`, `time`, `content`, `add_time`) VALUES
(37, '2', '硕士', '2013年工商管理专业（会计学方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '￥24000', '2013-03-02', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548866899379.png" /><img style="width:279px;height:53px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548866893539.jpg" width="304" height="62" />&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班工商管理专业</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（会计学方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对财务工作岗位职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办工商管理专业（会计方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>60<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">自然辩证法概论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="5" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代管理理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">战略管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">市场营销管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">财务管理理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">审计理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">会计理论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">人力资源管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理沟通</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:black;font-family:宋体;">管理会计前沿</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">员工关系管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">项目管理</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 105px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">报名及注册时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">开课时间</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1321</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2012</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1322</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1323</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">7</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px;border-style:none solid solid;border-color:#000000 black black;padding:0cm 7px;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">1324</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">—</span><span style="font-family:;">10</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td><td style="border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:none solid solid none;border-color:#000000 black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:170px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="170"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">年</span><span style="font-family:;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">月</span><span style="font-family:;">16</span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">日</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【收费标准】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学费</span><span style="font-family:;">24000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元（刷卡、现金、支票均可），报名费</span><span style="font-family:;">200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元，教材资料费</span><span style="font-family:;">1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">元；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">申请学位者参加硕士学位论文指导及答辩等费用，另按北京理工大学相关规定执行；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">进修班正式开课后，学员因故不能坚持进修，视作自动放弃学习，不退进修费。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">注：</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">2012</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">年</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">12</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">月</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">1</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">日前</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">报名学员执行学费</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;">20000</span></strong><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;">标准</span></strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【证书颁发】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、学员修完全部课程，并通过结业考试后，经北京理工大学研究生院审核颁发结业证书。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、获得学士学位满三年，已通过所学专业课程的考核与国家组织的全国统一水平考试，并公开发表一篇相关论文，即可以进入硕士学位申请阶段。通过学校论文答辩与学位审批后，可以获得北京理工大学管理学硕士学位。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【特别提醒】</span><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></strong></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;text-indent:35px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">交学校审核的所有证件材料等须是真实有效的，若因虚假材料造成一切后果由本人承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">申硕说明】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 32px;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">有关申请硕士学位事项按国务院学位委员会</span>[1998]54<span style="font-family:宋体;">号文件的规定和学校的相关规定执行。</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 15px 0px 0cm;text-align:left;line-height:27px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">增值服务】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可免费参加北京理工大学管理与经济学院主办的五次高水平讲座；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">本班学员可加入北京理工大学管理与经济学院校友会，拓宽人脉资源，参加丰富多彩的校友活动。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【联系方式】</span></strong><span style="color:navy;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名电话：</span>010-68918810&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;010-68918072&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;18701396872</span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">报名地点：北京理工大学（东门）管理与经济学院主楼二层</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span>224<span style="font-family:宋体;">室</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">联</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">系</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人：</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">钟老师</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">李老师</span></span></p><p style="line-height:27px;"><span style="font-family:;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 1354886731);
INSERT INTO `np_courses` (`cid`, `type`, `level`, `name`, `price`, `time`, `content`, `add_time`) VALUES
(38, '2', '硕士', '2013年工商管理专业（人力资源方向）在职研究生课程进修班', '￥24000', '2013-03-02', '<p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"><img title="clip_image001.png" src="/upload/20121207/13548867608012.png" /><img style="width:289px;height:56px;" title="clip_image003.jpg" src="/upload/20121207/13548867614017.jpg" width="317" height="69" /></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">2013</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">年在职研究生课程进修班工商管理专业</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;font-size:24px;">（人力资源方向）招生简章</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:red;font-family:宋体;font-size:19px;">（可申请管理学硕士学位）</span><strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">北京理工大学隶属于工业和信息化部，是一所理工为主、工理管文协调发展的全国重点大学，是新中国成立以来国家历批次重点建设的高校，首批设立研究生院，首批进入国家“211工程”和“985工程”建设行列。学校办学层次齐全，拥有学士、硕士、博士学位授予权和博士后流动站。七十多年来，学校为国家培养了大批高层次经济管理人才，深受社会的广泛赞誉。学校毕业生的就业率和社会评价，均居国内同类学科前列。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">为适应社会发展对高层次管理人才的需求，对接企业对人力资源工作岗位职业资格的需要，满足在职人员对知识更新与事业再造的要求，培养掌握坚实理论知识和实际业务技能的复合型人才，北京理工大学</span><span style="font-family:;">2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年继续在北京地区举办工商管理专业（人力资源方向）在职研究生课程进修班。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名条件】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、遵纪守法，品行端正，在教学、科研、专门技术、管理等方面做出一定成绩的在职人员。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、本科毕业并获得学士学位二年以上的人员</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">大专学历者可参加进修班学习，但不能申请硕士学位。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">3<span style="font-family:宋体;">、拟申请硕士学位的人员，须已获得学士学位并在获得学士学位后工作三年以上，或虽无学士学位但已获得硕士或博士学位者。已获得</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的学士、硕士或博士学位为国（境）外学位的，其所获的国（境）外学位需经教育部留学服务中心认证。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【招生名额】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:21px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">招生人数：</span>60<span style="font-family:宋体;">人</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【报名方式】</span></strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">1<span style="font-family:宋体;">、在线报名：登陆官网</span><a href="http://edp.bit.edu.cn/"><span style="color:#0000FF;font-family:calibri;">http://edp.bit.edu.cn</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;">；在</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">课程申请—在职研究生</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">模块中选择相应课程，在线填报</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体;">点击“我要报名”即可，经资格审查符合条件者，将寄发</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">2<span style="font-family:宋体;">、现场报名：携带身份证与最高学历毕业证、学位证书原件及复印件到北京理工大学主楼</span>219<span style="font-family:宋体;">室填写报名表，当场进行资格审查，符合条件者发放</span>“<span style="font-family:宋体;">入学通知书</span>”<span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">报名须知】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">报名时须携带以下证件：</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">学历证书原件、学位证书原件、本人身份证原件</span><span style="font-family:;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">复印件；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:;">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">张一寸本人近期彩色免冠照片；</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">网报学员需提交学历证、学位证扫描件发送到</span><span style="font-family:;">bjlgedp@163.com</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【培养方式】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0px 28px;text-indent:14px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">面授与自学相结合，学制两年，业余时间授课。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【特色优势】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:42px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．课程设置更务实&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2．教学团队更专业&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3．增值资源更丰厚&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4．全程服务更贴心</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:宋体;">【课程设置】</span></strong><strong><span style="color:#000066;font-family:;"></span></strong></span></p><table style="margin:auto auto auto 48px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" bordercolor="#000000" width="591"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课程类别</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:499px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="499" colspan="2"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">课&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;程&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;名&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;line-height:37px;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">公共课</span></strong></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">自然辩证法概论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">语言基础（英语）</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">科研诚信系列讲座</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="5" width="89"><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">学位课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">现代管理理论与方法</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">战略管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">市场营销管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">财务管理理论与方法</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">宏观经济学</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">微观经济学</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">人力资源管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">会计理论</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">品牌管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专利及知识产权保护</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:89px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" rowspan="2" width="89"><p style="margin:15px 0cm 0px;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">专业课</span></strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;"></span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">管理沟通</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">绩效与薪酬管理</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0cm;width:247px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="247"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">员工关系管理</span></p></td><td style="padding:0cm;width:252px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="252"><p style="text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">项目管理</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="text-indent:54px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">注：课程若有任何变化，以学院最新公布为准。</span><span style="font-family:;"></span></p><p><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:navy;font-family:宋体;">【开课时间】</span></strong><span style="color:red;font-family:;"></span></span></p><div align="center"><table style="margin:auto auto auto 36px;border:currentcolor;width:501px;border-collapse:collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="501"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:0cm 7px;border:1px solid black;width:132px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="132"><p style="text-align:center;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">班</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;">次</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:;"></span></strong></p></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 0px;border-style:solid solid solid none;border-color:black black black #000000;padding:0cm 7px;width:198px;background-color:transparent;" valign="top" width="198"><p style="text-align:center